original_title: Paw Patrol: Dino Rescue: Roar To The Rescue
overview: The PAW Patrol returns to the Dino Wilds for a roaring rescue! Mayor Humdinger is stuck on a runaway Brachiosaurus and a T-Rex is chomping everything in sight! Then, a Turbot family sightseeing expedition turns into a wild ride and more!
tagline: Paw Patrol - Roar to the Rescue
